quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  10,90,WE XHAWEZNA BIBENI ‘ISRA’ILEL-BEHRE FE’ETBE’AHUM FIR’AWNU WE XHUNUDUHU BEGJÆN WE’ADWEN HETTA ‘IDHA ‘EDREKEHUL-GAREKU KALE ‘AMENTU ‘ENNEHU LA ‘ILAHE ‘ILLAL-LEDHI ‘AMENET BIHI BENU ‘ISRA’ILE WE ‘ENA MINEL-MUSLIMINE
  10,91,‘AL’ANE WE KAD ‘ASEJTE KABLU WE KUNTE MINEL-MUFSIDINE
  10,92,FALJEWME NUNEXHXHIKE BIBEDENIKE LITEKUNE LIMEN HALFEKE ‘AJETEN WE ‘INNE KETHIRÆN MINE EN-NASI ‘AN ‘AJATINA LEGAFILUNE
  10,93,WE LEKAD BEWWE’NA BENI ‘ISRA’ILE MUBEWWE’E SIDKIN WE REZEKNAHUM MINET-TEJJIBATI FEMA EHTELEFU HETTA XHA’EHUMUL-’ILMU ‘INNE REBBEKE JEKDI BEJNEHUM JEWMEL-KIJAMETI FIMA KANU FIHI JEHTELIFUNE
  10,94,FE’IN KUNTE FI SHEKKIN MIMMA ‘ENZELNA ‘ILEJKE FAS’ELIL-LEDHINE JEKRE’UNEL-KITABE MIN KABLIKE LEKAD XHA’EKEL-HEKKU MIN RABBIKE FELA TEKUNENNE MINEL-MUMTERINE
  10,95,WE LA TEKUNENNE MINEL-LEDHINE KEDHDHEBU BI’AJATI ELLAHI FETEKUNE MINEL-HASIRINE
  10,96,‘INNEL-LEDHINE HEKKAT ‘ALEJHIM KELIMETU RABBIKE LA JU’UMINUNE
  10,97,WE LEW XHA’ET/HUM KULLU ‘AJETIN HETTA JEREWL-’ADHABEL-’ELIME
  10,98,FELEWLA KANET KARJETUN ‘AMENET FENEFE’AHA ‘IMANUHA ‘ILLA KAWME JUNIS LEMMA ‘AMENU KESHEFNA ‘ANHUM ‘ADHABEL-HIZJI FIL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA WE METTA’NAHUM ‘ILA HININ
  10,99,WE LEW SHA’E REBBUKE LE’AMENE MEN FIL-’ERDI KULLUHUM XHEMI’ÆN ‘EFE’ENTE TUKRIHU EN-NASE HETTA JEKUNU MU’UMININE
  10,100,WE MA KANE LINEFSIN ‘EN TU’UMINE ‘ILLA BI’IDHNI ELLAHI WE JEXH’ALU ER-RIXHSE ‘ALEL-LEDHINE LA JA’KILUNE
  10,101,KUL ENDHURU MADHA FI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE MA TUGNIL-’AJATU WE EN-NUDHURU ‘AN KAWMIN LA JU’UMINUNE
  10,102,FEHEL JENTEDHIRUNE ‘ILLA MITHLE ‘EJJAMIL-LEDHINE HALEW MIN KABLIHIM KUL FANTEDHIRU ‘INNI ME’AKUM MINEL-MUNTEDHIRINE
  10,103,THUMME NUNEXHXHI RUSULENA WEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU KEDHALIKE HEKKÆN ‘ALEJNA NUNXHIL-MU’UMININE
  10,104,KUL JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NASU ‘IN KUNTUM FI SHEKKIN MIN DINI FELA ‘A’BUDUL-LEDHINE TA’BUDUNE MIN DUNI ELLAHI WE LEKIN ‘A’BUDU ELLAHEL-LEDHI JETEWEFFAKUM WE ‘UMIRTU ‘EN ‘EKUNE MINEL-MU’UMININE
  10,105,WE ‘EN ‘EKIM WEXHHEKE LILDDINI HENIFÆN WE LA TEKUNENNE MINEL-MUSHRIKINE
  10,106,WE LA TED’U MIN DUNI ELLAHI MA LA JENFA’UKE WE LA JEDURRUKE FE’IN FE’ALTE FE’INNEKE ‘IDHÆN MINE EDH-DHALIMINE
  10,107,WE ‘IN JEMSESKEL-LAHU BIDURRIN FELA KASHIFE LEHU ‘ILLA HUWE WE ‘IN JURIDKE BIHAJRIN FELA RADDE LIFEDLIHI JUSIBU BIHI MEN JESHA’U MIN ‘IBADIHI WE HUWEL-GAFURU ER-REHIMU
  10,108,KUL JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NASU KAD XHA’EKUMUL-HEKKU MIN RABBIKUM FEMENI EHTEDA FE’INNEMA JEHTEDI LINEFSIHI WE MEN DELLE FE’INNEMA JEDILLU ‘ALEJHA WE MA ‘ENA ‘ALEJKUM BIWEKILIN
  10,109,WE ETTEBI’ MA JUHA ‘ILEJKE WE ESBIR HETTA JEHKUMEL-LAHU WE HUWE HAJRUL-HAKIMINE
  11,1,‘ELIF-LAM-RA KITABUN ‘UHKIMET ‘AJATUHU THUMME FUSSILET MIN LEDUN HEKIMIN HABIRIN
  11,2,‘ELLA TA’BUDU ‘ILLALLAHE ‘INNENI LEKUM MINHU NEDHIRUN WE BESHIRUN
  11,3,WE ‘ENI ESTEGFIRU REBBEKUM THUMME TUBU ‘ILEJHI JUMETTI’KUM META’ÆN HESENÆN ‘ILA ‘EXHELIN MUSEMMEN WE JU’UTI KULLE DHI FEDLIN FEDLEHU WE ‘IN TEWELLEW FE’INNI ‘EHAFU ‘ALEJKUM ‘ADHABE JEWMIN KEBIRIN
  11,4,‘ILA ELLAHI MERXHI’UKUM WE HUWE ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN KADIRUN
  11,5,‘ELA ‘INNEHUM JETHNUNE SUDUREHUM LIJESTEHFU MINHU ‘ELA HINE JESTEGSHUNE THIJABEHUM JA’LEMU MA JUSIRRUNE WE MA JU’LINUNE ‘INNEHU ‘ALIMUN BIDHATI ES-SUDURI